&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Concept used:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If the sum of the digits of a number is divisible by 9, then the number itself is divisible by 9.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Calculation:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Among the options given above, only the sum of digits of&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;12321 is divisible by 9.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1 + 2 + 3 + 2 + 1 = 9 which is divisible by 9&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence,&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;12321 is divisible by 9.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; &quot;&gt;&amp;there4;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;The correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;12321.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Given:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;A man sells two cows for Rs.15,640 each, gaining 15% on one and losing 15% on the other.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Concept used:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1.&amp;nbsp;Selling Price = Cost Price &amp;times; (1 + Gain%)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2.&amp;nbsp;Selling Price = Cost Price &amp;times; (1 - Loss%)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Calculation:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Cost price of the cow that&amp;#39;s sold at a 15% profit = 15640&amp;nbsp;&amp;divide; (1 +&amp;nbsp;15%) = Rs. 13600&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Profit incurred = 15640 - 13600 = Rs. 2040&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Cost price of the cow that&amp;#39;s sold at a 15% loss&amp;nbsp;= 15640&amp;nbsp;&amp;divide; (1 -&amp;nbsp;15%) = Rs. 18400&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Loss incurred = 18400 - 15640 = Rs. 2760&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Total loss&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; 2760 - 2040&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; Rs. 720&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; &quot;&gt;&amp;there4; His total loss is Rs. 720.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/shortcut-trick-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Shortcut Trick&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

